Hosties_Jail_Prizon_Remix_v4_0

By: DasSpix and Spaikku

Purpose:
This is primarily a prison break map with less restricted gameplay, but it can also be played for hosties.

Key Features:
-16 Prison Cells and 1 Special Cell
-One secret vent
-Swimming pool
-Big Cage
-Guarding Spaces
-Running Zone
-Shower room
-Armory with many weapons
-Gun cell, smoke granade cell

Have fun!
